usageInstructions: Place one at a time on the ground, light the fuse by its end and immediately retire at least 15m.
safetyDistancePublic: The public must be at least 25m away
unClassification: UN Classification: 0336 - Pyrotechnic articles for technical use
riskWarning: Explosive: fire, blast or projection hazard
productDescription: Box of 5 fuse thunder crackers producing an explosion of impressive intensity
